## 2) `/admin/users`

### Load
- `GET /admin/users`

### Fields nên render
- `id`
- `email`
- `fullName`
- `role`
- `status`
- `createdAt`

### Row actions
- Lock user:
  - `PATCH /admin/users/:userId/lock`
  - body:
```json
{ "locked": true }
```
- Unlock user:
  - `PATCH /admin/users/:userId/lock`
  - body:
```json
{ "locked": false }
```

